quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  7,117,WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA ‘EN ‘ELKI ‘ASAKE FE’IDHA HIJE TELKAFU MA JE’FIKUNE
  7,118,FEWEKA’AL-HEKKU WE BETELE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,119,FEGULIBU HUNALIKE WE ENKALEBU SAGIRINE
  7,120,WE ‘ULKIJE ES-SEHERETU SAXHIDINE
  7,121,KALU ‘AMENNA BIREBBIL-’ALEMINE
  7,122,REBBI MUSA WE HARUNE
  7,123,KALE FIR’AWNU ‘AMENTUM BIHI KABLE ‘EN ‘ADHENE LEKUM ‘INNE HADHA LEMEKRUN MEKERTUMUHU FIL-MEDINETI LITUHRIXHU MINHA ‘EHLEHA FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE
  7,124,LE’UKATTI’ANNE ‘EJDIJEKUM WE ‘ERXHULEKUM MIN HILAFIN THUMME LE’USELLIBENNEKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  7,125,KALU ‘INNA ‘ILA RABBINA MUNKALIBUNE
  7,126,WE MA TENKIMU MINNA ‘ILLA ‘EN ‘AMENNA BI’AJATI RABBINA LEMMA XHA’ETNA REBBENA ‘EFRIG ‘ALEJNA SEBRÆN WE TEWEFFENA MUSLIMINE
  7,127,WE KALEL-MELE’U MIN KAWMI FIR’AWNE ‘ETEDHERU MUSA WE KAWMEHU LIJUFSIDU FIL-’ERDI WE JEDHEREKE WE ‘ALIHETEKE KALE SENUKATTILU ‘EBNA’EHUM WE NESTEHJI NISA’EHUM WE ‘INNA FEWKAHUM KAHIRUNE
  7,128,KALE MUSA LIKAWMIHI ESTA’INU BILLAHI WE ESBIRU ‘INNEL-’ERDE LILLAHI JURITHUHA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WEL-’AKIBETU LILMUTTEKINE
  7,129,KALU ‘UDHINA MIN KABLI ‘EN TE’TIJENA WE MIN BA’DI MA XHI’TENA KALE ‘ASA REBBUKUM ‘EN JUHLIKE ‘ADUWEKUM WE JESTEHLIFEKUM FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURE KEJFE TA’MELUNE
  7,130,WE LEKAD ‘EHADHNA ‘ALE FIR’AWNE BIS-SININE WE NEKSIN MINE ETH-THEMERATI LE’ALLEHUM JEDHDHEKKERUNE
  7,131,FE’IDHA XHA’ET/HUMUL-HESENETU KALU LENA HEDHIHI WE ‘IN TUSIBHUM SEJJI’ETUN JETTEJJERU BIMUSA WE MEN ME’AHU ‘ELA ‘INNEMA TA’IRUHUM ‘INDEL-LAHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  7,132,WE KALU MEHMA TE’TINA BIHI MIN ‘AJETIN LITESHERENA BIHA FEMA NEHNU LEKE BIMU’UMININE
  7,133,FE’ERSELNA ‘ALEJHIMUT-TUFANE WEL-XHERADE WEL-KUMMELE WE ED-DEFADI’A WE ED-DEME ‘AJATIN MUFESSELATIN FASTEKBERU WE KANU KAWMÆN MUXHRIMINE
  7,134,WE LEMMA WEKA’A ‘ALEJHIMU ER-RIXHZU KALU JA MUSA ED’U LENA REBBEKE BIMA ‘AHIDE ‘INDEKE LE’IN KESHEFTE ‘ANNA ER-RIXHZE LENU’UMINENNE LEKE WE LENURSILENNE ME’AKE BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  7,135,FELEMMA KESHEFNA ‘ANHUMU ER-RIXHZE ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN HUM BALIGUHU ‘IDHA HUM JENKUTHUNE
  7,136,FANTEKAMNA MINHUM FE’EGREKNAHUM FIL-JEMMI BI’ENNEHUM KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA WE KANU ‘ANHA GAFILINE
  7,137,WE ‘EWRETHNAL-KAWMEL-LEDHINE KANU JUSTED’AFUNE MESHARIKAL-’ERDI WE MEGARIBEHA ELLETI BAREKNA FIHA WE TEMMET KELIMETU RABBIKEL-HUSNA ‘ALA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE BIMA SEBERU WE DEMMERNA MA KANE JESNA’U FIR’AWNU WE KAWMUHU WE MA KANU JA’RISHUNE
  7,138,WE XHAWEZNA BIBENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-BEHRE FE’ETEW ‘ALA KAWMIN JA’KUFUNE ‘ALA ‘ESNAMIN LEHUM KALU JA MUSA EXH’AL LENA ‘ILEHÆN KEMA LEHUM ‘ALIHETUN KALE ‘INNEKUM KAWMUN TEXHHELUNE
  7,139,‘INNE HA’UULA’ MUTEBBERUN MA HUM FIHI WE BATILUN MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,140,KALE ‘EGAJREL-LAHI ‘EBGIKUM ‘ILEHÆN WE HUWE FEDDELEKUM ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  7,141,WE ‘IDH ‘ENXHEJNAKUM MIN ‘ALI FIR’AWNE JESUMUNEKUM SU’EL-’ADHABI JUKATTILUNE ‘EBNA’EKUM WE JESTEHJUNE NISA’EKUM WE FI DHALIKUM BELA’UN MIN RABBIKUM ‘ADHIMUN